text:
My highest recommendations!  How nice it is when one has very high expectations and they are still exceeded :).
A summary:
- very friendly and professional Italian family running the place;
- atmosphere of relaxation / tranquility / indulgence - really puts one in the holiday mood
- very very good breakfasts :).  They have a great combination of some Italian touches and the local produce; excellent presentation and taste; nice veranda to linger over food and coffee;
- there is swimming pool - I did not use it though;
- room was very comfortable, great sleep quality;
- location was good as well - close to the center but away from the noise - gives some local feel;
- high attention to detail (beach towels, etc).
Thank you for a wonderful stay :).
